-----
- rtklib_sp3_driver.c
    Our (AGPL-3.0-only) C driver. Calls RTKLIB readsp3() + peph2pos().
- generate_sp3_interp_reference.sh
    Our (AGPL-3.0-only) regeneration script.
- igs16296.sp3
    Vendored SP3-c precise-ephemeris file (input; see below).
